{"tid":1977732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"AMC院線破產 萬達王健林電影夢碎","createTime":"2020-04-18T07:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T11:46:10.000Z","uid":32511,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0350c364eee1d6421d4d5c2bcecb24ebe3c5c9c2","tid":1977732,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情衝擊全球影業，有媒體指出，大陸萬達集團旗下、美國最大院線AMC正與律所接觸，探討可能的破產事宜。<br />\n <br />\n香港經濟日報報導，萬達於2012年以26億美元收購AMC全部股權，當時萬達董事長王健林曾揚言要在2020年，達到全球20％的電影市佔率。但隨後因大陸對其的監管限制及萬達縮減海外投資，萬達對AMC的持股降至38％，但仍為萬達子公司。<br />\n <br />\n由於新冠肺炎疫情在美國持續擴散，AMC早前宣布全球1,000間影院將暫時關閉，包括首席執行官在內的600名員工暫時停職。<br />\n <br />\n報導表示，暫未知AMC是否有聘請其他顧問以進行重組，但破產非常有可能因AMC已開始無力承擔租金。有指AMC債務高達49億美元，面臨債務違約風險。評級機構標普則在4月7日將AMC的信用評級從B降至CCC-級，即發債人可能會違約。<br />\n <br />\n不過萬達在17日發公告澄清，AMC沒有申請破產，消息純屬謠言。<br />\n <br />\n而專注大陸國內市場的萬達電影，第一季也巨虧人民幣（下同）5.5億元～6.5億元之間。2019年，王健林的財富已經縮水超680億元，跌出中國富豪榜前十名單，如今疫情之下，市場預測王健林的財富會繼續大幅縮水。"},{"pid":"03b7db4001933ac0cabe3c27ad696722935f6c7d","tid":1977732,"uid":78470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"佢個二世祖而家點"},{"pid":"7970e365830942b956ca96a7d549c6d5b2eddc82","tid":1977732,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3edcd085061600ccc536140ecf7afdf575f998","tid":1977732,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"萬達對AMC的持股降至38％<br />\n即係仲有好多人陪葬"},{"pid":"ded924086766b3d09f740870aa76a841090728f8","tid":1977732,"uid":290118,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:39:35.000Z","msg":"王健林咪同馬雲呢啲一樣係condom嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e368e7289c24e1ef17422a407ad257a9eb5d2ca4","tid":1977732,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"渣既"},{"pid":"961f812a2ad12dec6af20032dae0ffda51fcd170","tid":1977732,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c3edcd085061600ccc536140ecf7afdf575f998","tid":1977732,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"萬達對AMC的持股降至38％<br />\n即係仲有好多人陪葬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:40:07.000Z","msg":"搵到咁多水魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314f2ab2755290c2a688454eeaf33d764e294f82","tid":1977732,"uid":16830,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"曾經做過中國首富嘅都冇好下場, 祝你好運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係好似馬雲咁上繳公司提早退休 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d0d7be6b9cbee46c9b2e7296c0aeea92c0f357","tid":1977732,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:41:31.000Z","msg":"支那根本一直債冚債 , 停兩個月都頂唔到"},{"pid":"0687fbbf8cc899c361db648c48f4edddc21fd2b2","tid":1977732,"uid":65663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03b7db4001933ac0cabe3c27ad696722935f6c7d","tid":1977732,"uid":78470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"佢個二世祖而家點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"打機洗到幾多 溝少幾個藝人就得啦"},{"pid":"0c41ee3116d53f9ec353ba16115a8abd80d1cebc","tid":1977732,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"馬雲一退休全家生癌"},{"pid":"a9d83051f9157f03069e1506dfc01fe38b5a88eb","tid":1977732,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"王健林自己都被中共清算啦"},{"pid":"2670e24